ass=\"line\">show_debug_message(b[2]);//6</div><div class=\"line\"></div><div class=\"line\">b[@ 2] = 7;//此时改变的是新的数组</div><div class=\"line\"></div><div class=\"line\">show_debug_message(a[2]);//5</div><div class=\"line\">show_debug_message(b[2]);//7</div><div class=\"line\"></div><div class=\"line\">//-------------------------------------------------</div><div class=\"line\"></div><div class=\"line\">a[1] = 1;</div><div class=\"line\">a[2] = 2;</div><div class=\"line\">a[3] = 3;</div><div class=\"line\">a[4] = 4;</div><div class=\"line\"></div><div class=\"line\">b = a; //获取a的所有数据</div><div class=\"line\">b[5] = 2;// 移动一位，并创建新的数组</div><div class=\"line\"></div><div class=\"line\">b[@ 2] = 5;//此时不会再改变数组a的值</div><div class=\"line\"></div><div class=\"line\">show_debug_message(a[2]);//2</div><div class=\"line\">show_debug_message(b[2]);//5</div><div class=\"line\"></div><div class=\"line\">a[2] = 4; //一维数组</div><div class=\"line\">a[0,1] = 5;//二维数组</div><div class=\"line\"></div><div class=\"line\">show_debug_message(array_length_2d(a,0));//3(0,1,2)</div><div class=\"line\">show_debug_message(a[0,2]);//4</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","text":"数组的accessors。12345678910111213141516171819202122232425262728293031323334353637var a,b,c;a[2] = 4;show_debug_message(a[2]);//4b = a;b[@ 2] = ","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[{"name":"教程","slug":"教程","count":7,"path":"api/categories/教程.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"GMS教程","slug":"GMS教程","count":3,"path":"api/tags/GMS教程.json"}]},{"title":"参数之间传值","slug":"course/参数之间传值","date":"2016-04-11T12:14:04.000Z","updated":"2017-04-22T13:44:55.591Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/course/参数之间传值.json","excerpt":"<p>最近用到一种功能，需要用到数组大量定义一系列数据，又不想重复定义，因此想调用上一个定义的参数里面的数据，发现GMS的参数之间是并发运行的，互相之间无法通信。下面讨论这个问题，怎么给函数传递多个参数，并且让参数之间可以通信。</p>","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":null,"text":"最近用到一种功能，需要用到数组大量定义一系列数据，又不想重复定义，因此想调用上一个定义的参数里面的数据，发现GMS的参数之间是并发运行的，互相之间无法通信。下面讨论这个问题，怎么给函数传递多个参数，并且让参数之间可以通信。1234567891011121314151617181